
Descriptions of some of the files
=================================


NooneCurves.py

    The main Noone curves calculation in Python

NooneCurves_Ends.py

    The main Noone curves calculation in Python, with the addition of
    dumping the delta versus q plot start and end points.

Plot_noone_curves_delp_0.0.pdf

    An example plot with delp set to 0

Plot_noone_curves_delp_-10.0.pdf

    An example plot with delp set to -10

Plot_noone_curves_delp_-30.0.pdf

    An example plot with delp set to -30

set_parms

    An example of setting parameters in a file to over ride the values
    set in the main NooneCurves.py file

Run_example

    An example of running NooneCurves.py with new values for parameters
    on the command line (with = signs) as well as a parameter setting
    file written as standard Python assignments

